OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe doctors of Hall Green Health
OL,7,     Fcome face to face with some rare
OL,8,     Fconditions. It's a reminder that
OL,9,     Fwhen you're a GP, you never know
OL,10,     Fwhat is going to walk through your
OL,11,     Fdoor.
OL,12,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,14,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,15,     Funder the microscope. John checks
OL,16,     Fover a man who fell six feet on to
OL,17,     Fconcrete and may have complex
OL,18,     Ffractures.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
