OL,5,G2100 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,7,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,8,     Fpassengers, at least one of whom
OL,9,     Fis bleeding heavily, and a
OL,10,     F13-year-old cyclist suffers a
OL,11,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FParamedics race to High Wycombe
OL,14,     Fwhere a handyman has fallen 18
OL,15,     Ffeet from a ladder, risking
OL,16,     Fcatastrophic internal injuries.
OL,17,     FElsewhere, 53-year-old Paula has
OL,18,     Fhad a suspected stroke.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
