OL,5,G0105 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FWith appointments lasting just 10
OL,7,     Fminutes, our GPs have the
OL,8,     Fdifficult task of deciding what to
OL,9,     Fprioritise and what can safely
OL,10,     Fwait for another day.
OL,11,G0210 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FDr Nick Mani receives a critically
OL,13,     Fill one-day-old baby, and cricket
OL,14,     Flegend Dickie Bird is in for a
OL,15,     Ffollow-up. Documentary series
OL,16,     Ffilmed inside Barnsley casualty
OL,17,     Fdepartment.
